They ask how you're feeling.

1236
00:57:01,371 --> 00:57:03,492
Because you know better than the doctor how you're feeling.

1237
00:57:04,132 --> 00:57:06,352
But the doctor doesn't often ask you how to solve the problem,

1238
00:57:06,593 --> 00:57:08,333
because they're better equipped than you to do that.

1239
